The paper deals with the Maximal Independent Set (MIS) problem in distributed graph algorithms, which falls under the category of Distributed Computing (cs.DC) and Distributed Data Structures (cs.DS). The paper also involves graph theory (cs.GT) and probabilistic analysis (cs.LG), as well as algorithms (cs.AL).
